|     |      | 2H  |     | 5-card suit, #NF#,
                           [nobr]#see {warning} below#
|     |      | 2S  |     | cue-bid, GF
|     |   2+<| 2NT,3C,3D <| min, NF
|     |      | 3H  |     | 5-card suit, GF
