|  2H   | 2S | natural, F1
|  ?    |    |
|  2NT  |    | 3*{H}, #short {S}#, min, NF
|  3m   |    | 3*{H}, 5\|6*m, #short om#, NF
| !3om! |    | #4*{H}, max, GF#
|  3H   |    | 4*{H}, min, NF
|  3S   |    | 4*{S}, min, NF
|  3NT  |    | 3*{H}, #short {S}#, max
| !4om! |    | splinter, 4*{S}, max
| !4H!  |    | 4*{H}, max, "`__I forgot about 3om__{thinsp}`"
| !4S!  |    | no splinter, 4*{S}, max
|===

